data.description: Come check out this beautiful four bedroom, two and half bath home. This house offers hardwood floors and granite counter tops. The living room is spacious with a gas log fireplace perfect for the family to come together and relax.  The master bedroom is very spacious. The master bathroom has granite counter tops, double sinks, a walk-in shower, and a large garden tub. The upstairs offers three bedrooms and a bathroom.
